description: [``botocore``] This release adds support for UpdateContactFlowMetadata, DeleteContactFlow and module APIs. For details, see the Release Notes in the Amazon Connect Administrator Guide.
[``botocore``] Added new S3 endpoint settings to allow to convert the current UTC time into a specified time zone when a date partition folder is created. Using with 'DatePartitionedEnabled'.

[``botocore``] This release adds an optional parameter dry-run for the UpdateElasticsearchDomainConfig API to perform basic validation checks, and detect the deployment type that will be required for the configuration change, without actually applying the change.
[``botocore``] Adds new parameter to CreateActivation API . This parameter is for "internal use only".
[``botocore``] Added new APIs for enabling Echo Reduction with Voice Focus.
[``botocore``] Adding missing exceptions to RegisterCluster operation
[``botocore``] Add support for Exasol data source, 1 click enterprise embedding and email customization.
[``botocore``] This release include SDK changes for the feature launch of Stack Import to Service Managed StackSet.
[``botocore``] Adds local backup support to Amazon RDS on AWS Outposts.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for Amazon Braket Hybrid Jobs.
[``botocore``] Added Amazon CloudWatch publishing option for S3 Storage Lens metrics.
[``botocore``] Add new APIs for managing Datasets, Changesets, and Dataviews.
